node.text: We are so excited to partner with @liberationstationbookstore - a black-owned, globally-recognized children's bookstore! Today's reading of "Shady Baby" is by the Founder and CEO, Victoria Scott-Miller. Snuggle up with your little ones (on your Nugget, of course), and enjoy!

node.text:
From pulling to stand to taking first steps - Nugget can help your babies on the move! We've enlisted the help of occupational therapist Bree Milani from @_sproutandthrive to give you the best recommendations for your baby! ⁠
⁠
On today's episode we talk about cruising (side stepping) around the Nugget. Cruising is a mini milestone that helps build strength for first steps! Check out our stories for more and let us know how you have used Nuggets to help your baby develop ↓

node.text:
Today we’re lucky to be joined by @thekiaramel from Drag Queen Story Hour Raleigh, to read two books that teach us about pride and identity: Our Rainbow from @littlebeebooks and @glaad, and My Rainbow by DeShanna and Trinity Neal (@trinitysmamabear), and @art_twink. 

Before COVID-19, many of @dqshraleigh’s events took place at the LGBT Center of Raleigh (@lgbtcenterofraleigh). As part of our partnership this month, we’re donating $10,000 to the Center — if you enjoy this story time, we hope you’ll consider donating too. You can find a link to the center by tapping the link in our bio and selecting yesterday’s rainbow mural image.

NOTE: To celebrate and enjoy this fun event, we will be leaving the comments section turned on, however, comments that do not respect others and stray from our community guidelines will be taken down. You can find our community guidelines in the FAQ section of our site.

node.text: As thousands of happy families already know, Nuggets are great for getting the push and pull of proprioceptive play. But with our factory operating slower than usual as we cautiously navigate Covid-19, we know not everyone who wants a Nugget has one just yet. Thankfully, @candokiddo has come to the rescue! On the newest episode of OT Nugget, Rachel talks about her kiddos' motor play area, and how to create your own — for any home, and any budget.

node.text: One of the best add-ons to encourage additional Nugget play is one of the cheapest things around — blue painter’s tape! This week for OT Nugget, Rachel from @candokiddo shows off four simple games that you can play at home with just a Nugget and a roll of blue painter’s tape. As always, try it on your own and share with us using the tag #OTNugget! Have fun!

node.text: Tired of saying “No!” to indoor activities like jumping, crashing, smashing and rolling? @candokiddo has an idea: use the Nugget to give a clear and constructive “yes.”

node.title: Why you should say “yes” to indoor play

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Nugget on August 19, 2021 tagging @luckyspilledmilk. May be an image of bedroom.

node.text: The double-brushed, double-release is here! Blueridge 🏔and Willow 🍃are now available in the shop, in Nuggets, Cover Sets, and Pillow Packs. Let us know which one you got in the comments below 👇⁠

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Nugget on August 19, 2021 tagging @petiteslunes. May be an image of 2 people, child and indoor.

node.text:
Today's the day! Willow and Blueridge will be available to shop today at 12pm ET! We can't wait to see them in your homes in a few short weeks. 🤩⁠⁠
⁠⁠

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Nugget on August 18, 2021 tagging @margaret.wright, and @sunwoven. May be an image of child, indoor and text that says 'THE IN Nillow! MAGIC BOL'.

node.text: It's double the double-brushed fun this week! Introducing Willow, a verdant, forest green as perfectly serene as a leisurely picnic on a warm afternoon. Available in the Nugget Shop starting tomorrow, Thursday Aug 19 at noon ET.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Nugget on August 18, 2021. May be an image of outdoors.

node.text: CLAIMED!! There's a certain magic that sets in before the change in seasons, that moment of suspended time when it's not quite summer, but not yet fall. That last summer picnic at the park, or a meandering bike ride with friends. A moment of calm and coziness before the start of something new. We've captured that essence in our latest color, Willow, and today, @tweedlebeedle is the only place to find it.⁠ Summerville Nuggeteers, today is your day! There is one Nugget on hand at your local family-owned shop, Tweedle Beedle, and the first person to make an in-person purchase will take it home. NOTE: please travel carefully and observe all local safety precautions, including masking up! For those not in Summerville, stay tuned to our IG stories as we reveal our cozy new color.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Nugget on August 17, 2021 tagging @kayandcrew. May be an image of 1 person, child and indoor.

node.text: What's better than one double brush release?⁠⁠

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Nugget on August 17, 2021 tagging @nelldeutsch. May be an image of 1 person, child and indoor.

node.text: We're excited to introduce you to our latest double-brushed microsuede, as cozy as the campsite after a long day on the trails 🏕 Say hello to Blueridge, a classic, grounded navy inspired by the Blueridge Parkway in our home state of NC—home to photographers, explorers and outdoor enthusiasts alike. Adventures await, starting 8/19.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Nugget on August 17, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, standing and outdoors.

node.text: CLAIMED!! Grab your hiking boots, backpack and water bottle because we're headed to the mountains for some outdoor adventures. 🏔Western NC Nuggeteers — today is your lucky day! @Playdategoods in Asheville NC was founded by parents and husband-wife team Logan and Francesca after their son Enzo was born, and today, Playdate Goods is the only place to get our latest Nugget color: BLUERIDGE. Francesca has one Nugget on hand at the shop, and the first Nugget fan to make an in-person purchase at Playdate will win the prize. While we love to take in the sights on our hikes, this is one trail you might want to take at a fast pace. NOTE: please travel with care, observe all local safety precautions, and remember your mask. For those not in Asheville, follow along on our IG stories as we reveal the newest color in the Nugget lineup!

node.accessibility_caption: A bright orange box with the words Nugget written on the side of it. A yellow duck sits on top of it. Written on the top of the page are the words: “We’ve had babies, kids, husbands, and dogs in a Nugget, but have we done duck on a nugget?”

node.text: Ok, which one of you silly gooses posted this? (It was simenstad218 on Twitter) 🦆

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Nugget on August 12, 2021. May be an image of child and indoor.

node.text:
It's that time of year again! The school year is set to start, and with it, a new program from Nugget in support of leaders and advocates for children in communities across the country: public school teachers.⁠ Introducing: The More You Nugget! 🍎📚 This program places nearly-perfect Nuggets in public school K-5 classrooms. ⁠⁠
⁠⁠
Head to the link in our bio to learn all about the program and to nominate a teacher!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Nugget on August 10, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, child and indoor.

node.text:
Time to put on a show 🎵⁠⁠
⁠⁠
We asked longtime fan @bringingupbabe for some of her favorite builds and activities. From belting our their favorite tunes to scaling Nugget Mountain in an elaborate obstacle course - this mom and daughter pair know how to have fun! ⁠⁠
⁠⁠
Head to the link in our bio for more & let us know which build has been on repeat in your home lately 👇⁠⁠
